title: Civil War - House of M 01-05 (2008|Digital|Zone-Empire)
description:
This is a great follow-up to the House of M event that shows that universe's effects in relation to the Civil War. Promotional info for the collected edition - "The biggest House of M story is finally revealed: how did Magneto take over the world? He began life as a penniless refugee, but rose to conquer the entire planet... and now Christos Gage (Thunderbolts, House of M: Avengers) and Andrea Di Vito (Annihilation) show you how the Master of Magnetism did it! Witness Magneto's first battle with the Sentinels...the tragic end of his marriage...and his fight against Apocalypse for leadership of all mutants! The secret history of the House of M unfolds here!"

All issues are digital copies thanks to Zone-Empire. Please seed, and enjoy! :-)
